title: Kedai Kopi 328
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Fast food, Take-out, Taiwanese, Malaysian
description: Banner reads 阿良鐵板燒. Food stall in Millennium Kobusak, in a housing area near CKS supermarket, re-opened Mar 2016. The owner is a vegetarian who used to live in Taiwan. Makes vegetarian fare with Taiwanese style as well local cuisine: hot noodles, curry laksa, nasi lemak, porridge, braised tofu, and more. Operating since 2012.
